parameters: Kru "Just as I expected, there are quite a lot of monsters."
Umi "Yeah. But you're strong. Umi doesn't have to do anything."

Kru "No, that's not true. But one has to be strong. Otherwise, you can't
survive... That much is certain..."
Kru "Does Umi live with Mia-chan alone?"
Umi "Yes. Kaka and Toto are dead."
Kru "I see. Sorry to hear that."
Kru (Umi... She's still just a child... She's been through a lot.)
Umi "It's not bad. Do you have Toto and Kaka?"

Kru "Mine? I don't have either. I was an orphan, so I don't even know if
they're alive or dead."
Umi "...I just thought... you might be the same as Umi..."
Kru "Eh... Ah... You did work hard."
Umi "U... Mi... will sleep... a bit..."
Kru "She's already asleep... She must be really tired..."
Kru "But still... to be able to sleep in a place like this..."
Kru "Alright! Then let's go full throttle to the back of the cave!"
Kru "No, I'm fine! Look at me!"
Umi "No... Umi's eyes can't be deceived."
Umi "Umi heals wounds. So she can see wounds..."
Umi "Umi can see wounds... Everyone has wounds..."
Umi "Yeah... That's why sometimes you feel down."
Kru "That's true... There are times when you feel down."
Umi "Right... It's bad to force yourself when you're not feeling well."
Umi "Yes... Umi is also not feeling well... So..."
Kru "Eh!? You're going to sleep again!"
Umi "That can wait. Getting better comes first."
Umi "I've put up a barrier. You... should sleep too."
Umi "If you sleep... you'll mostly... get better..."
Kru "She's already asleep... She's a mysterious girl..."

Kru (Everyone... has wounds, huh... I'm sure mine haven't healed yet
either...)
Kru (And... surely this girl has her own wounds too...)
Kru "...Eh?... She can put up barriers?"
Kru "Then why didn't she just put up a barrier from the start?"
Kru "You've slept enough. Come on, let's go..."
